    RapidOcrOnnx
    https://github.com/RapidAI/RapidOcrOnnx
    Copyright (c) the RapidAI / RapidOcrOnnx contributors.
    Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

Modifications include:
  * Upgrade of the OCR pipeline to PaddleOCR PP-OCRv6.
  * Replacement of the orientation model with PP-LCNet_x1_0_textline_ori.
  * Embedded-models build mode (single-file DLL, no external .onnx).
  * Extended C ABI (OcrInitEmbedded, OcrDetectMem, per-block getters).
  * Statically linked ONNX Runtime and OpenCV, static CRT (/MT).
  * Table recognition: SLANet Plus + img2table + MinerU IoU matching.


